{"tid":1457311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要贏民意既入黎睇睇 - 機場旅客同小朋友十分肚餓","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:48:07.000Z","uid":560,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"14771c2192039d50add83fe13763bcde57235752","tid":1457311,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"多得啲解散軍，機場landing開始恢復正常<br />\n但所有鋪頭都落哂閘（除禁區）換句話說裡係出面既所有人都冇補給<br />\n<br />\n因為解散軍吹風動用武力清場令商鋪提早收工<br />\n呢家只要有手足帶野入黎派就可以贏盡掌聲<br />\n<br />\n反正之前啲家長咁多劵係手 大家快啲帶補給入黎<br />\n<br />\n利申：留守係機場 希望各位手足幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ca22064f2520d38fbb1c904e01c2dc272bafe6","tid":1457311,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c255c3baaa4b4df7861bd1d1bae77e4b6580c764","tid":1457311,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"重返機場既手足 唔該你帶物資 <br />\n就算唔俾手足都俾旅客 講聲sorry."},{"pid":"003d5aabe77ed8def5514ada9ba82a1b7659601d","tid":1457311,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:43:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"443372f8693d79b2e564dc5737b92034432e4edd","tid":1457311,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:50:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f161a003f308a3de49fb42e5d4cbc13fdb38843","tid":1457311,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80a93f38d868d4d63c7fb085ed92c991a6e4724a","tid":1457311,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid